```systemverilog
property p_req_ack;
  @(posedge clk) disable iff (!rst_n)
    $rose(req) |-> ##[1:4] (ack [*2] ##1 !ack);
endproperty
assert property (p_req_ack);
```
$rose(req) triggers on rising edge. ##[1:4] allows 1-4 cycle delay. ack [*2] requires ack high for two consecutive cycles. ##1 !ack ensures it deasserts afterward.
